    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E92 M3 features the legendary S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8, delivering linear power delivery up to its 8,400 RPM redline. Equipped with a precise 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory-spec M Variable Differential Lock, this chassis provides exceptional lateral grip and communicative steering feedback. The vehicle retains its structural integrity with the weight-saving carbon fiber roof and features a well-sorted suspension setup. Recent preventative maintenance includes rod bearing inspection and throttle actuator servicing, ensuring the high-revving valvetrain remains robust. A driver-focused example with minimal aesthetic patina, optimized for the purist.",
