      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle strikes the perfect balance between performance and practicality. The exterior finish retains its deep luster, with only minor, age-appropriate blemishes that are hardly noticeable upon casual inspection. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of comfort; the premium seating surfaces are in excellent shape with minimal bolster wear, and all electronic features\u2014from the dual-zone climate control to the premium infotainment system\u2014function flawlessly. Mechanically, this car is exceptionally sound, having received regular synthetic oil changes and all manufacturer-scheduled maintenance. It drives smooth and quiet, with responsive handling and a robust powertrain that inspires confidence on both city streets and highways. The tires have plenty of tread remaining, and the brakes provide firm, consistent stopping power. Whether you're commuting daily or planning a long-distance road trip, this car offers a premium, reliable experience. Includes a complete folder of service records, the original owner's manual, and two sets of keys.",
